A line of AOE spells that take way too much mana for their damage output and are considered a waste of mana.<br>
<br>
Translocates as a way to help others since they complained to Verant about a lack of people to port them.  Remember that porting people who arn't in our XP group can't be considered an &quot;In Character&quot; act, so it's only to benefit others.<br>
